First Step:
  go to:
      https://myaccount.google.com/lesssecureapps?utm_source=google-account&utm_medium=web
  Make sure that your google account allows third part app

We need some jar files in order to sent emails

1. CommonsEmails.Jars folder
    - commons-email-1.3.jar
    - javax.mail-1.4.5-sources.jar
    - javax.mail-1.4.5.jar

2. File >> Project Structure >> Libraries >> click on ' + ' button
3. Select and add the 3 jars files.